<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <!-- Vignette Ads -->
    <%- include('./Global/ads/vignette.ejs'); %>
    <!-- Google Tag -->
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DRAMA STORE - Welcome</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.0/css/all.min.css"
          integrity="sha512-10/jx2EXwxxWqCLX/hHth/vu2KY3jCF70dCQB8TSgNjbCVAC/8vai53GfMDrO2Emgwccf2pJqxct9ehpzG+MTw=="
          crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <style>
        /* --- Global Styles --- */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        main {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* --- Hero (First Viewport) --- */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #1e90ff;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
        }

        /* --- Join Us Button --- */
        .joinus {
            background-color: #1e90ff;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 18px 4px;
            margin: 16px auto;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .joinus sup {
            font-size: xx-small;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .joinus:hover,
        .joinus:active {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border: 2px solid #1e90ff;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* --- Article Section --- */
        .content-article {
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content-article h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #1e90ff;
        }

        .content-article p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .content-article p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .content-article h2 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section / First Viewport -->
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Welcome to DRAMA STORE</h1>
            <p>
                Discover the latest and greatest Korean dramas. 
                Join our Telegram channel for updates!
            </p>
            <div class="joinus" onclick="window.open('tg://join?invite=mTx_t-6TBx9hNTc8', '_self')">
                <i class="fa-brands fa-telegram"></i> JOIN US ON TELEGRAM <br>
                <sup>Korean series updates on Telegram</sup>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Article Section -->
        <section class="content-article" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
            <h2>The Beauty of Korean Dramas</h2>
            <p>
                Korean dramas (K-Dramas) have taken the world by storm for their unique blend of romance, 
                emotion, and immersive storytelling. Each series brings a fresh perspective, whether itâ€™s 
                a light-hearted comedy set in Seoul, a historical romance in the Joseon era, or a thrilling
                crime investigation.
            </p>
            <p>
                What truly sets K-Dramas apart is the cultural richness they offer. Viewers get a taste of 
                Korean customs, language, food, and family values woven seamlessly into each storyline.
                This cultural flair, combined with high production quality and well-crafted plots, makes 
                for an experience that keeps fans coming back for more.
            </p>
            <p>
                From heartwarming dramas that explore deep personal connections, to action-packed series 
                that keep you on the edge of your seat, the world of K-Dramas is vast and inviting. 
                At DRAMA STORE, we are committed to bringing you these stories right at your fingertips 
                through our Telegram channel, ensuring you never miss an episode of your favorite show.
            </p>
            <p>
                So sit back, relax, and let these stories transport you to another world. 
                Happy watching and we hope you enjoy your stay at DRAMA STORE!
            </p>
            <br>
            <h2>New Released Episodes</h2>
            <ul style="list-style: circle; color: #444;">
                <% latest_episodes.forEach(ep => { %>
                 <li>Episode <%= String(ep.epno).padStart(2, '0') %> - <%= ep.drama_name %></li>
                <% }) %>
            </ul>
            <br><br>
            <h2>Most Trending Dramas This Month in DRAMA STORE</h2>
            <ul style="list-style: circle; color: #444;">
                <% popular.forEach(drama => { %>
                 <li><%= drama.newDramaName %></li>
                <% }) %>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>